<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.1.3">
<l>mēvā varakkar teṉṉilaṅkai vēntaṉ vīyac caramturantu</l>
<l>māvāy piḷantu mallaṭarttu marutañ cāytta mālatiṭam</l>
<l>kāvār teṅkiṉ paḻamvīḻak kayalkaḷ pāyak kurukiriyum</l>
<l>pūvār kaḻaṉi yeḻilārum puḷḷam pūtaṅ kuṭitāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of Māl who, having shot arrows</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the king of the enemy demons of Lanka of the south died,</l>
<l>Having split the horse’s mouth [and] destroyed the wrestlers,</l>
<l rend="indent">toppled the marutu [trees],</l>
<l>Is Puḷḷampūtankuṭi, full of loveliness [from] flower-filled fields,</l>
<l rend="indent">where herons flee</l>
<l>When the kayal fish jump, as fruit falls from coconut [trees]</l>
<l rend="indent">which fill the groves.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
